==Features==
{| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size: smaller; text-align: center; width: auto; table-layout: fixed"
|-
! Video player
! Outbound streaming
! Skinnable
! Media database
! [[gapless playback|Gapless]] audio decoding
! [[music visualization|Visualizer]]
! Remote controllable
! Intelligent playlists from database (based on criteria)
! [[High-dynamic-range imaging|HDR video playback]]
! Stereoscopic 3D Playback
! 360-degree video playback
